text: Sariya Mahrupovna Zakyrova (, , born 10 April 1964) is a Russian rower. She competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Russian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the Soviet Union Category:Olympic rowers of the Unified Team Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Naberezhnye Chelny Category:Tatar sportspeople
